{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-tsx","path":"/algorithm-baekjoon-10996/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p><strong>본 포스팅은 정답이 아닙니다. 저 스스로 푼 답이며, 문제를 푸는 사람마다 접근 방식이나 풀이가 다를 수 있습니다.</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><strong>문제:</strong> </p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>예제를 보고 규칙을 유추한 뒤에 별을 찍어 보세요.</p>\n</blockquote>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>입력:</strong></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>첫째 줄에 N(1 ≤ N ≤ 100)이 주어진다.</p>\n</blockquote>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>출력:</strong></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>첫째 줄부터 차례대로 별을 출력한다.</p>\n</blockquote>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>예제 입력:</strong> </p>\n<blockquote>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">1</code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">2</code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">3</code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">4</code></pre></div>\n</blockquote>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>예제 출력:</strong> </p>\n<blockquote>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">*</code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">*\n *\n*\n *</code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">* *\n *\n* *\n *\n* *\n *</code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">* *\n * *\n* *\n * *\n* *\n * *\n* *\n * *</code></pre></div>\n</blockquote>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"풀이\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%ED%92%80%EC%9D%B4\" aria-label=\"풀이 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><